QuestData.Title: Tapping the Underground
QuestData.Description: Have you seen them, $n?$B$BThese are not ordinary murlocs. They have been drawn by the ley line that flows from Azsuna into this land. $B$BSomehow they have managed to tap into its arcane current and are tapping its power for their own devious purposes.$B$BThese disturbances must be stopped if the ley line is to remain intact.
QuestData.LogDescription: Destroy Seerspine Conduits in the Murloc Shoals.
